posting_body: ['Wayzata Woods', '240 Central Ave.', 'N, Wayzata, MN, 55391', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'WAYZATA WOODS', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 790 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Wayzata Woods Apartments in Wayzata, Minnesota.', 'Wayzata Woods is a well-maintained community nestled in a quiet neighborhood of mature landscaping and charming buildings.', 'Lake Minnetonka is within walking distance from your new home with Downtown Wayzata just minutes away.', 'Easy access to I-394 and just minutes from downtown Minneapolis/St Paul, MSP International and Ridgedale Mall.', 'Enjoy our private walking path to the Colonial Square where you can shop Lunds & Byerly’s and other local businesses.', 'Wayzata Woods combines an amazing location with a host of great extras which include:', '-Fully appointed Kitchens', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Fitness Center', '- Heated Underground Parking', '- Walking Paths', '- Sparkling Pool', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pets: We are happy to accept those “other members” of your family with additional deposit.', 'Features', '- Spacious Floor Plans', '- Disposal', '- Central Heating', '- Air Conditioner', '- Refrigerator', '- Dishwasher', '- Countertop Stoves', 'Community Amenities', '- On-Site Management', '- Fitness Center', '- Walking Paths', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Pool', '- Heated Underground Parking', 'Driving Directions', 'Located behind Park Nicollet Medical Center', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', '$300 Pet Fee and $300 Pet Deposit per cat or dog.', '$35 monthly pet rent per pet.', 'Maximum 2 pets per apartment.', 'Breed and weight restrictions apply.', 'tofH7O8E']
